‚Ä¢	Used aggregate functions to summarize total visits and chronic disease counts
‚Ä¢	Applied CASE logic to classify chronic vs non-chronic encounters
‚Ä¢	Exported cleaned results to Excel
Analysis & Visualization (Excel / Tableau)
‚Ä¢	Performed final data checks and formatting
‚Ä¢	Built calculated fields for chronic burden ratios
‚Ä¢	Applied Top 10 filters for prioritization
‚Ä¢	Developed clear bar chart visuals for leadership review
